WEBVTT

00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:09.980
=Rise of Her Lady Physician=

00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:12.340
=Episode 18=

00:00:12.380 --> 00:00:14.940
=There Is Something Between You Two!=

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:16.600
You are so clever.

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:18.960
I'm afraid you didn't enter the palace

00:00:19.120 --> 00:00:20.440
just to practice medicine, right?

00:00:27.280 --> 00:00:28.560
I wouldn't dare to deceive you.

00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:32.360
I do have my own reasons.

00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:34.880
I only want to uncover

00:00:35.080 --> 00:00:37.240
the truth about my mother's
accusation of harming you.

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:39.840
But I absolutely have no intention
of harming you.

00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:42.000
Silly girl.

00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:43.600
These past few days,

00:00:43.960 --> 00:00:45.880
you've served me so well.

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:47.800
I've

00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:49.400
seen it with my own eyes

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:50.840
and kept it in my heart.

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:53.040
You're a good girl.

00:00:54.440 --> 00:00:55.360
These past few days,

00:00:56.120 --> 00:00:56.960
I've also been

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:58.840
thinking about

00:00:59.040 --> 00:00:59.880
how your mother

00:01:00.920 --> 00:01:01.760
treated my illness

00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:03.560
ten years ago.

00:01:04.800 --> 00:01:06.100
To be honest,

00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:07.710
some things

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:09.550
really don't make sense.

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:11.680
Your Majesty,

00:01:12.320 --> 00:01:14.200
my mother was always a kind person.

00:01:14.530 --> 00:01:15.910
She would never harm you.

00:01:16.840 --> 00:01:18.120
I've checked the medical records.

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:19.620
The treatment methods she used

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:21.400
are all recorded in medical books,

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:22.960
absolutely no mistakes.

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:24.720
Your Majesty.

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:26.520
You fell into a coma back then.

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.760
Something must've been off.

00:01:30.160 --> 00:01:31.360
That incident

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:33.520
is indeed full of doubts.

00:01:34.400 --> 00:01:35.240
If someone dared

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:38.040
to frame your mother in the palace,

00:01:39.080 --> 00:01:40.160
it'd mean that she

00:01:40.520 --> 00:01:42.600
must have spied on their secrets.

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:45.680
Even I got implicated in it.

00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:49.560
I'm afraid the implications

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:52.160
are far-reaching.

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:55.440
If you want to survive in the palace,

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:57.720
don't bring up this matter again.

00:01:58.320 --> 00:01:59.160
Do you understand?

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:03.240
This may be dangerous,

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:05.160
but as her daughter,

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:08.560
if I cannot clear her name,

00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:11.600
I'll regret it for the rest of my life.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:15.240
Your Majesty,

00:02:15.880 --> 00:02:17.880
I promise I won't act recklessly.

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:20.400
Please rest assured.

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:21.880
Never mind.

00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:24.000
Just remember.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:25.840
Only when

00:02:26.040 --> 00:02:27.560
you are alive can there be hope.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.330
Help me put on

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:35.160
that gold hairpin.

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:39.120
Aye.

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:56.600
Look.

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:58.760
You're so good at this, young girl.

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:09.240
Have you heard of

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:10.960
the funny story about Her Majesty?

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:12.400
What funny story?

00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:15.720
I heard

00:03:15.920 --> 00:03:16.920
she has grown muddle-headed,

00:03:17.480 --> 00:03:19.440
even worse than a three-year-old kid!

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:21.340
I heard

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:22.760
she wets her pants every day!

00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:24.640
She can't even hold her urine!

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:26.080
Is that true?

00:03:26.180 --> 00:03:27.040
If it's true,

00:03:27.050 --> 00:03:28.400
it'll be so hilarious!

00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:32.720
You... You...

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:33.680
You filthy servants!

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:35.880
How...

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:36.960
How dare you

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:38.640
insult me?

00:03:42.600 --> 00:03:43.440
Your Majesty!

00:03:43.880 --> 00:03:44.720
Your Majesty!

00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:46.360
Your Majesty!

00:03:47.720 --> 00:03:48.580
Help!

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:50.500
Her Majesty fainted!

00:03:52.240 --> 00:03:53.080
Mother.

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:54.440
Mother!

00:03:55.160 --> 00:03:56.000
Mother!

00:03:56.680 --> 00:03:57.640
Wake up, Mother!

00:03:58.320 --> 00:03:59.160
Mother!

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:00.800
What happened?

00:04:01.480 --> 00:04:02.440
Why did she faint?

00:04:03.080 --> 00:04:03.940
Your Majesty,

00:04:03.960 --> 00:04:05.800
I don't know what method
Attendant Rong used.

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:07.680
When she was walking
in the Imperial Garden,

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:09.080
she suddenly vomited fresh blood

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:09.960
and fainted!

00:04:10.280 --> 00:04:11.800
We couldn't wake her up!

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:13.920
Rong Zelan.

00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:15.480
I'm so disappointed!

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:17.000
Guards!

00:04:17.840 --> 00:04:18.920
Drag Rong Zelan out!

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:20.200
Tomorrow at 12:45,

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:21.160
behead her in public!

00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:23.080
Your Majesty, it's not true!

00:04:23.200 --> 00:04:24.040
- Silence!
- Her...

00:04:24.760 --> 00:04:26.200
How dare you still deny it?

00:04:26.200 --> 00:04:27.040
Your Majesty!

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:28.440
Attendant Rong has worked so hard.

00:04:28.880 --> 00:04:29.800
Something must be off!

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:31.560
Please give her a chance

00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:33.320
to explain the truth.

00:04:33.320 --> 00:04:34.160
Silence!

00:04:35.240 --> 00:04:36.080
Whoever pleads for her

00:04:37.080 --> 00:04:37.920
will also be punished!

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:40.160
Drag her out!

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:42.200
Your Majesty, I'm innocent!

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:44.240
Your Majesty!

00:04:44.400 --> 00:04:45.240
Your Majesty!

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:05.000
Attendant Rong!

00:05:10.520 --> 00:05:11.360
Lord Song.

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:12.480
Is Her Majesty awake?

00:05:13.640 --> 00:05:14.490
No.

00:05:14.560 --> 00:05:15.400
Not only that.

00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:17.000
The two maids who were present

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:19.200
both mysteriously
fell into the lake and died.

00:05:20.280 --> 00:05:21.120
There are rumors

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:22.520
in the palace that

00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:23.520
Her Majesty has become

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:25.240
irritated because of old age

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:27.760
and can't even control her urination.

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:30.440
The rumors are harsh.

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:35.080
They say she's too old

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:36.360
to hold her urine,

00:05:36.920 --> 00:05:38.240
bringing shame to the royal family.

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:40.200
The rumors are so disgraceful.

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:42.520
Someone must be behind the whole thing.

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:47.440
Perhaps the person wants to

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:49.560
to provoke Her Majesty

00:05:49.720 --> 00:05:50.680
and make her faint

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:51.960
to frame me

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:53.160
and cast me out.

00:05:54.280 --> 00:05:55.400
If that's the case,

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:58.360
I must not let them get what they want.

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:00.920
The priority

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.600
is to make Her Majesty
regain consciousness.

00:06:04.280 --> 00:06:05.680
Lord Wu has tried every means.

00:06:07.240 --> 00:06:08.080
It didn't work.

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:13.720
Lord Song,

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:15.440
I can perform Soul-fixing Needle,

00:06:16.280 --> 00:06:18.280
which is very effective against
energy exhaustion.

00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:20.360
Perhaps I can save Her Majesty.

00:06:20.760 --> 00:06:21.720
Soul-fixing Needle?

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:23.680
Isn't it your family's

00:06:23.760 --> 00:06:24.920
secret skill that only men can learn?

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:28.440
You...

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:30.720
Are you a man or a woman?

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:33.480
Can you stop joking at this point?

00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:36.720
Lord Song,

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:39.480
please help me secure a chance
to perform acupuncture on Her Majesty.

00:06:42.200 --> 00:06:43.040
Okay.

00:06:43.240 --> 00:06:44.240
I'll talk to His Majesty

00:06:44.600 --> 00:06:45.440
and try to persuade him.

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:47.000
Before the execution,

00:06:47.320 --> 00:06:48.280
I'll definitely get you out.

00:06:49.640 --> 00:06:50.480
Thanks, Lord Song.

00:06:52.960 --> 00:06:53.800
No need.

00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:55.560
If

00:06:56.600 --> 00:06:58.280
you really want to thank me,

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:00.200
- you can...
- You've saved my life.

00:07:00.440 --> 00:07:01.280
I have to thank you.

00:07:27.120 --> 00:07:27.960
Your Majesty!

00:07:28.080 --> 00:07:29.480
I'm not skilled enough

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:31.200
to awaken Her Majesty!

00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:33.680
Please punish me!

00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:38.880
Your Majesty, I have something to report!

00:07:39.020 --> 00:07:39.860
Go ahead.

00:07:39.880 --> 00:07:41.560
Rong Zelan has the secret skill,
Soul-fixing Needle.

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:42.920
Maybe she can do it.

00:07:43.320 --> 00:07:44.760
Please postpone the execution!

00:07:45.920 --> 00:07:46.760
It's her again.

00:07:47.600 --> 00:07:48.440
Ridiculous!

00:07:48.640 --> 00:07:50.400
The needle skill is passed down
only to men.

00:07:50.760 --> 00:07:52.680
How could she, a woman, have learned it?

00:07:53.190 --> 00:07:54.060
Your Majesty,

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:55.880
this is clearly a scheme to delay time.

00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:57.000
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:07:57.640 --> 00:07:59.600
Her Majesty once disliked this attendant.

00:08:00.080 --> 00:08:00.920
You can't trust her.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:03.840
Her Majesty's condition is critical.

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:05.000
When Her Majesty is awake,

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:06.480
you can still punish her.

00:08:07.040 --> 00:08:07.880
Your Majesty,

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:09.120
although I have doubts,

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:11.000
there is no other way at present!

00:08:11.640 --> 00:08:13.360
Please allow her to do it!

00:08:14.280 --> 00:08:15.120
Your Majesty,

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:17.600
Attendant Rong has spared no effort
to take care of Her Majesty.

00:08:18.440 --> 00:08:19.360
Please have mercy.

00:08:22.320 --> 00:08:23.160
Officer Song.

00:08:23.760 --> 00:08:26.600
You've repeatedly defended Rong Zelan.

00:08:27.520 --> 00:08:28.360
Could it be

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:30.720
there's something between you and her?

00:08:31.200 --> 00:08:32.040
That's right.

00:08:32.720 --> 00:08:34.480
Officer Song
has been on the attendant's side.

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:36.160
It's truly puzzling.

00:08:36.720 --> 00:08:37.560
Ridiculous!

00:08:38.720 --> 00:08:40.800
There's nothing between us.

00:08:41.080 --> 00:08:42.080
This is simply because

00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:43.880
I'm concerned about Her Majesty,

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:45.880
fearing that it might be too late
to save her.

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:48.600
Bring her here.

00:08:49.880 --> 00:08:50.740
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:06.200
Rong...

00:09:07.640 --> 00:09:08.480
Where is she?

00:09:08.520 --> 00:09:09.360
Where is she?

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:10.660
My lord, she was

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:11.720
sent to the execution ground.

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:13.480
Who allowed you to take her away?

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:15.200
We were only obeying the order.

00:09:17.680 --> 00:09:18.520
Get off me!

00:09:19.640 --> 00:09:20.480
Get off me!

00:09:33.900 --> 00:09:34.740
(Order)

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:37.000
Do you want to be executed?

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:40.680
Let's go.

00:10:12.200 --> 00:10:13.040
Her finger moved!

00:10:38.520 --> 00:10:39.360
Mother.

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:41.000
How are you feeling?

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:45.280
Everyone out!

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:46.960
Stay away from me!

00:10:47.320 --> 00:10:48.160
Out!

00:10:51.220 --> 00:10:52.100
Mother!

00:10:52.120 --> 00:10:52.960
Everyone out!

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:54.560
I only want

00:10:54.720 --> 00:10:56.400
Rong Zelan to stay.